[
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000000_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000000_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "So sit down here at my feet and rest your bright head on my lap, that I may not see in your young eyes the shadows my story will bring across their bonny blue.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000001_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000001_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "So I went joyfully though my mother grieved to part with me; she had little to love save me, my father, Conrad Montressor, having been lost at sea when but three months wed",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000002_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000002_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "Therefore I took heart of grace when I thought of my dark face and spindling shape, hoping that when I should be grown up I might be counted not unworthy of my race.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000003_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000003_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "The Place was an old-fashioned, mysterious house, such as I delighted in, and mrs Montressor was ever kind to me, albeit a little stern, for she was a proud woman and cared but little for children, having none of her own.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000007_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000007_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "Though I spoke not of it to anyone, I had a great longing to see my Uncle Hugh's wife, concerning whom I had heard much, both good and bad.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000008_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "My Uncle Hugh, albeit the oldest of the family, had never married until now, and all the countryside rang with talk of his young wife.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000008_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000008_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "Yet, being somewhat keener of comprehension than they knew, I heard and understood not a little of their talk.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000010_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000010_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "Some had much to say of her pride and insolence, and wondered if mrs Montressor would tamely yield her mistress ship to the stranger.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000012_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000012_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "But my aunts and their stepmother talked much of Alicia, and they spoke slightingly of her, saying that she was but a light woman and that no good would come of my Uncle Hugh's having wed her, with other things of a like nature.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000014_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000014_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "The hall was lighted by small, square paned windows, and at its end a little flight of steps led up to the Red Room.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000015_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000015_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "It was mrs Montressor's sitting room then, where she wrote her letters and examined household accounts, and sometimes had an old gossip in to tea.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000018_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000018_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "\"There, there, little Beatrice!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000018_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000018_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "Did I frighten you, child?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000018_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000018_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "Forgive an old woman's thoughtlessness.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000019_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000019_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "But mrs Montressor saw to it that I obeyed her, and I went no more to the Red Room, but busied myself with other matters.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000020_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000020_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "For there were great doings at the Place and much coming and going.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000020_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000020_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "My aunts were never idle; there was to be much festivity Christmas week and a ball on Christmas Eve.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000020_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000020_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "And my aunts had promised me-though not till I had wearied them of my coaxing-that I should stay up that night and see as much of the gaiety as was good for me.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000020_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000020_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "So I did their errands and went early to bed every night without complaint-though I did this the more readily for that, when they thought me safely asleep, they would come in and talk around my bedroom fire, saying that of Alicia which I should not have heard.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000030_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000030_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "I had often in my own mind pictured this, my first meeting with Alicia, now in one way, now in another, but never had I dreamed of her speaking to me at all, so that it came to me as a great surprise when she turned and, holding out her lovely hands, said very graciously:",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000034_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000034_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "Nor could I think, though to me the thought seemed as treason, that she loved her husband overmuch, for she seemed half condescending and half disdainful to him; yet one thought not of this in her presence, but only remembered it when she had gone.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000036_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000036_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "When she paused by me and asked me lightly of what I was dreaming, since I had such a sober face, I answered her truly that it was of her-whereat she laughed, as one not ill pleased, and said half mockingly:",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000037_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000037_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "But come with me, child, if you will, for I have taken a strange fancy to your solemn eyes.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000038_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000038_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "And, though I understood not her meaning, I went, glad to see the Red Room once more.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000038_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000038_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "So she made me sit down and talk to her, which I did, for shyness was no failing of mine; and she asked me many questions, and some that I thought she should not have asked, but I could not answer them, so 'twere little harm.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000039_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000039_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "After that I spent a part of every day with her in the Red Room.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000042_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000042_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "When Christmas Eve drew nigh my silly head was full of the ball day and night.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000042_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000042_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "But a grievous disappointment befell me, for I awakened that day very ill with a most severe cold; and though I bore me bravely, my aunts discovered it soon, when, despite my piteous pleadings, I was put to bed, where I cried bitterly and would not be comforted.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000042_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000042_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "For I thought I should not see the fine folk and, more than all, Alicia.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000043_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000043_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "But that disappointment, at least, was spared me, for at night she came into my room, knowing of my longing-she was ever indulgent to my little wishes.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000043_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000043_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "And when I saw her I forgot my aching limbs and burning brow, and even the ball I was not to see, for never was mortal creature so lovely as she, standing there by my bed.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000044_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000044_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "Yet it could not be denied they were of wondrous beauty, white as polished marble.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000047_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000047_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "Then she leaned down to me until her splendid eyes looked straight into my dazzled ones.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000049_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000049_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "I found my voice and told her truly that I thought her beautiful beyond my dreams of angels-as indeed she was.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000049_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000049_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "Whereat she smiled as one well pleased.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000051_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000051_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "Then said he, \"Sweet, will you grant me a favour?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000052_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000052_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "And she answered, \"It may be that I will.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000053_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000053_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "And he said, \"Do not dance with that man tonight, Alicia.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000053_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000053_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "I mistrust him much.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000054_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000054_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "His voice had more of a husband's command than a lover's entreaty.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000056_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000056_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "He laughed and his brow cleared, though he said still sternly, \"Do not try me too far, Alicia.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000058_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000058_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "After that my aunts also came in, very beautifully and modestly dressed, but they seemed to me as nothing after Alicia.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000059_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000059_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "I had been straitly charged to stay in bed, which I did not, but got up and put on a gown.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000061_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000061_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "john, the gardener, had killed it, and I verily thought that if it had a soul, it must have gotten into this man.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000062_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000062_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "Nor did she shrink from his embrace, but even smiled and leaned nearer to him with a little smooth motion, as they talked to each other in some strange, foreign tongue.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000063_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000063_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "I was but a child and innocent, nor knew I aught of honour and dishonour.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000064_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000064_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "And as I watched them-not thinking of playing the spy-I saw her face grow suddenly cold, and she straightened herself up and pushed away her lover's arms.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000067_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000067_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "My uncle turned to Alicia, and very calmly and terribly he said, \"From this hour you are no longer wife of mine!\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000068_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000068_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "And there was that in his tone which told that his forgiveness and love should be hers nevermore.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000069_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000069_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "Then he motioned her out and she went, like a proud queen, with her glorious head erect and no shame on her brow.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000071_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000071_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "But my Uncle Hugh kept his word, and Alicia was no more wife to him, save only in name.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000071_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000071_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "Yet of gossip or scandal there was none, for the pride of his race kept secret his dishonour, nor did he ever seem other than a courteous and respectful husband.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000072_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000072_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "As for me, no one dreamed I knew aught of it, and I kept my own counsel as to what I had seen in the blue parlour on the night of the Christmas ball.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000073_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000073_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "After the New Year I went home, but ere long mrs Montressor sent for me again, saying that the house was lonely without little Beatrice.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000075_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000075_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "But every day I was with Alicia in the Red Room, where she would talk to me, oftentimes wildly and strangely, but always kindly.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000078_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000078_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "In the afternoon I was sitting in the wing hall, dreaming wondrous day dreams, when Alicia called me to the Red Room.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000078_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000078_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "Her hand, when she took mine, was burning hot, and her voice had a strange ring.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000079_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000079_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "\"Come, little Beatrice,\" she said, \"come talk to me, for I know not what to do with my lone self today.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000079_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000079_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "Time hangs heavily in this gloomy house.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000079_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000079_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "I do verily think this Red Room has an evil influence over me. See if your childish prattle can drive away the ghosts that riot in these dark old corners-ghosts of a ruined and shamed life!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000079_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000079_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "I mean not all I say-my brain seems on fire, little Beatrice.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000079_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000079_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "Come; it may be you know some grim old legend of this room-it must surely have one.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000079_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000079_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "Tush! never be so frightened, child-forget my vagaries. Tell me now and I will listen.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000080_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000080_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "Whereat she cast herself lithely on the satin couch and turned her lovely face on me.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000080_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000080_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "But his mother went mad with her remorse, and was kept a prisoner in the Red Room until her death.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000083_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000083_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "And I, remembering what I had seen in the blue parlour, was silent-for I could not lie.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000083_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000083_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "So she flung my hand away with a bitter laugh, and picked lightly from the table anear a small dagger with a jewelled handle.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000084_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000084_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "It seemed to me a cruel looking toy and I said so-whereat she smiled and drew her white fingers down the thin, shining blade in a fashion that made me cold.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000085_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000085_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "\"Such a little blow with this,\" she said, \"such a little blow-and the heart beats no longer, the weary brain rests, the lips and eyes smile never again!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000085_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000085_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "'twere a short path out of all difficulties, my Beatrice.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000087_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000087_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "\"Little, grave eyed Beatrice, tell me truly, would it grieve you much if you were never again to sit here with Alicia in this same Red Room?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000090_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000090_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "\"Now go,\" she said.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000091_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000091_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "Then she gently put me from the room, and I sat musing by the hall window until night fell darkly-and a fearsome night it was, of storm and blackness.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000092_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000092_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "Nor was the night blacker than his face, and he took no heed of me as I ran after him, thinking selfishly of the sweetmeats he had promised to bring me-but I thought no more of them when I got to the door of the Red Room.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5000_30597_000093_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5000/30597/5000_30597_000093_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5000",
        "content": "Alicia stood by the table, hooded and cloaked as for a journey, but her hood had slipped back, and her face rose from it marble white, save where her wrathful eyes burned out, with dread and guilt and hatred in their depths, while she had one arm raised as if to thrust him back.",
